At a large gathering in Saint Peter’s Square the Pope whispered to Donald Trump, "I bet you $100 with one wave of my hand I can make the crowd go crazy. It will be a celebration like you have never seen before, Mr. Trump.”

The Pope proceeded to slap him and the crowd went wild.
